AllMatters Menstrual Cup (OrganiCup)
description:
• Medical-grade UNDYED silicone
  • The only menstrual cup certified hypoallergenic with AllergyCertified
  • Registered with The Vegan Society
  • FDA registered
  • Made in Germany
  • Cup satisfaction guarantee

The AllMatters vision is #NEWPERIOD. In 3 years, you can use 792 tampons / pads or 1 AllMatters menstrual cup.

Menstrual cups are a wonderful reusable period product that can be used and reused for years. Silicone is derived from quartz, which is the second most abundant mineral in the Earth's crust and not hazardous to the environment. The menstrual cup is not coloured, avoiding any colouring additives.

When inserted correctly, you will not feel any discomfort and will be unable to tell that you have a cup inserted.

Size does not depend on anatomy. It depends on how much flow the cup can hold.

Packaging
The menstrual cup packaging is made from recyclable carton and instructions are printed directly onto the packaging to minimise waste. 

How to insert
Find out which fold you are most comfortable with - the C-fold and the Punchdown fold are our favourites! Make sure you maintain a firm grip on the cup and insert the cup tilted diagonally towards the back (towards your tailbone). Make sure that the cup is fully open by running your finger around the base of the cup to check for any folds.

VIDEO: HOW TO MAKE SURE YOUR MENSTRUAL CUP IS FULLY OPEN

VIDEO: HOW TO USE A MENSTRUAL CUP

How to remove
Reach your fingers in and find the base of the cup. Press down on the base of the cup to break the "seal" and pull the cup out. Maintain a firm grip of the cup. Do not pull hard on the stem to remove the cup as you will feel resistance. Use the stem as a guide to find the base of the cup.

Sterilising
Sterilise the cup before and after your period. Simply get a small bowl, place your cup inside, and pour hot water over to soak for 5 minutes.

Cleaning tips!
Use clean water and a fragrance-free soap or our fragrance-free multi-use OrganiWash to wash out. Rinsing with water every time you empty it will help prevent stains in the long run and keep your cup looking fresh! If the cup changes in colour or texture (becomes slimy), or changes in appearance in any way, stop use immediately.

Hygiene
Menstrual cups are very hygienic because no external factors or free oxygen will reach the accumulated menstrual flow while the cup is inserted, and no bacteria will be created. Wash your hands with soap before you insert or remove the cup and you should empty your menstrual every 8-12 hours, or earlier depending on your flow.

A 2019 report by the Lancet Public Health also concluded that menstrual cups are a safe option.

Disclaimer
If you have any pre-existing health conditions or if you are using an IUD, check with a doctor before use.

Cup satisfaction guarantee
As the official distributor of AllMatters products in Singapore, we offer their generous cup satisfaction guarantee. After trying the cup for min. 90 days, you can request a cup size exchange. To claim this, you must have a receipt from our website or partner stockists.  

Further terms of our website and sales can be found here.

 

You can buy AllMatters in Singapore at www.bamboostrawgirl.com, we are the only stockist for the original OrganiCup in Singapore. OrganiCup Singapore.

Aloe Kitchen Dish Soap Bar
description:
Tough on kitchen grease, Gentler on your overworked hands.

Not sure how to use a solid dish block to wash your dishes? Watch this video with all the tips on how you can get your dishes squeaky clean with the least soap and water.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wxPcfmlVYoo

The all natural grease fighting kitchen dish soap that is not only a more sustainable choice for our planet doing away with the plastic liquid detergent bottle, it is kinder to your hands with its 100% natural formulation enriched with fresh aloe vera. Squeaky clean dishes without synthetic chemicals or fragrances.

Unscented. Just smells clean. A kitchen decor on its own.  
Important Note: Do not trash the milk carton packaging it comes in. Just invert it with the spout facing down and viola you have a free soap dish, compliments from us.

Weight: +/- 125g
Dimensions: ~7cm x 6.5cm x 2.5cm

TIPS FOR USING:
- Wet sponge or cleaning brush. Rub sponge or brush across soap block several times.
- Squeeze sponge gently a few times for water and soap to interact to activate the lather.
- Clean dishes as you normally would.
- Repeat as needed.

Ancienet Grain Clusters - Apple Cinnamon 35g
description:
Less than 65 Kcals per serving. 

The clusters are made up of tiny popped Sorghum seeds, like mini popcorns - but better!

Traditionally, sorghum has been utilized globally in different types of cuisine, from the use of sorghum flour to make Roti in India to the fermentation of the grains in Chinese Baijiu (白酒). 

These apple-flavored clusters will bright up your life. Eat them straight from the bag as a snack or mix them with your favorite type of milk to start your day!

Snack guilt-free with our plant-based Ancient Grain Clusters.

name: Aomori Essential Oil Roll-On Perfume
description:
Wake up in the beautiful Japanese countryside to freshly brewed green tea, and take a deep breath as you look out over the serene view of Sakura blossoms in full bloom. Surround yourself with beautiful natural landscapes, and escape the busy city life.  

Note Profile:

    • Top: Yuzu, Hinoki
    • Middle: Green Tea, Sakura
    • Base: Cypress

The Wanderlust Series is a celebration of adventure, vibrant design, and the spirit of travel. Each essential roll-on is crafted with a blend of essential oils and jojoba oil, and these little tubes are packed full of evocative scents that will transport you to a different land. 

 

The Aomori Essential Oil Roll-On Perfume combines all the fragrances you would come to expect as you explore the panoramic landscapes of this city.  Without a doubt, the earthy aroma of the Hinoki essential oil is guaranteed to take you straight to Aomori, Japan.

Yuzu Essential Oil:


Slightly tart and slightly sweet, fresh, and light, the distinct, citrusy fragrance of the Yuzu essential oil may only make you crave for a Yuzu sake. The smell of Yuzu fruit blends well with other fragrances in this perfume, giving you that unique Japanese travel experience. 

Green Tea Essential Oil:


Bringing a sense of calm, the sweet, fresh, and minty scent of the green tea essential oil also sharpen your mental focus. As such, among the many green tea benefits is that it can be an excellent aid when studying or completing that important work assignment.

Sakura Essential Oil:


Inhale the fresh sweet aroma of cherry blossoms as you see them by the sakura trees in your surroundings. The floral scent of the sakura essential oil is subtle and delicate, reminding you of the blushing warmth of springtime.

Cypress Essential Oil:


Rounding up with fresh, herbaceous, and evergreen undertones, the distinct aroma of cypress essential oil creates a feeling of security and grounding. You can’t help but imagine the strength of cypress trees as you inhale their aromatic influence on the blend.

description: Varietally pure and gorgeously perfumed, the wine shows lychee, pineapple, Turkish Delight, and subtle spice notes on the nose. It's equally attractive on the palate, offering succulent fruit intensity combined with a silky mouthfeel, leading to a persistent flavorsome finish. At its best: now to 2023.

name: Ataahua Pinot Noir 2018 (Organic)
description: Grown from 20 + year old vines and organically farmed and produced. This is a stunning pinot, the 2018 harvest benefited from a growing season that was slightly cooler than the previous vintage, resulting in fully developed complex flavors. This is apparent from the first sip. This pinot has a bouquet of sweet berry fruit and cherries with notes of earthy forest floor and mushrooms. On the palate, it's elegant, well balanced, and has a long lingering finish, with just a touch of oak. Delicious when served with red meat dishes and particularly good with duck and mushroom risotto. The flavors in this wine develop beautifully in the wine glass.

name: Avant Garde Soap Dish - Rose
description:
Our dream soap dish that we found after our 3 year pursuit of the perfect one. Helped many new and lapsed bar soap users successfully transition to the new habit and make their bars last longer.

We name this range Avant Garde for its unconventional look, but don't be fooled. This soap dish ticks off almost every criteria on our requirement for that perfect soap dish. This is the brainchild of a talented artist in California @ProspandPop who had generously given us permission to replicate and sell this design in this part of the world.

A contemporary design that is highly functional.

- Angled slope allows water on bar to drain off easily.
- Foothold lets bar sit securely on the dish.
- Generous grooves minimise full contact with soap, allowing more surfaces to dry between showers.
- Grooves access are wide enough for fingers, for easy pick up of bars even when they are stuck to the dish.
- Simple lines and absence of cavities make cleaning a breeze.
- High durability.

Desert Rose

name: Beco Cod & Haddock Complete Dry Dog Food, 12kg
description: This cod & haddock recipe is low in fat and high in omega 3 & 6. It’s a grain-free recipe filled with freshly prepared fish, vegetables and superfoods, great for dogs with sensitive stomachs. Nothing artificial. We slow-cook our recipes between 90 - 120 ̊C so every bite contains the same protein, vitamins, oils and flavours of the original ingredients. Not only does that mean they’re delicious, it provides a diet that’s full of nutritional goodness, with the convenience of dry food. The nutritional balance of this recipe makes it perfect for older dogs or those trying to lose some weight. We have specifically chosen wild-caught fish species from fisheries that are deemed to support healthy populations. The Cod and Haddock population from the North Atlantic - FA027, has been monitored by independent bodies and is currently deemed to be productive and healthy.

name: Black or White
description:
Black or White? Neither. Cos these days, it is no longer easy to tell which is the correct way and which is not. Especially in the areas of sustainability, is a new cotton tote bag better than a disposable single use plastic bag? Is an electric car better than our regular car that runs on petrol? But what about the end of life battery? What are the 'costs' of their disposal and will it cost the planet more than what it replaced?

More often than not, we have no definite answers. As a consumer, we do not have the means to measure or verify the true life cycle costs of a product that we buy or use. Our biggest fear is that we jump into new solutions only to create a bigger issue later, unintentionally.

Nothing is black or white....we may never know which is the best solution. So the mantra that we follow, is as Sir Attenborough suggests, just don't waste.

Reuse what we already own to the maximum they can offer, repurpose or upcycle if they serve a good new purpose, else rehome to better hands. All else fails, recycle if viable, if not, please dispose and not add to unnecessary carbon and load to the recycling chain.

Buy what we need and want, but do that mindfully. Choose quality, something that will last and we will enjoy for a long time. Let your dollars have a voice for your choice and our planet.

These are guidelines we remind ourselves...and strive to do better at. And we hope this bar gives all of us a gentle nudge to LOOK UP, evaluate impacts in a bigger picture so we can all make the best informed decision.

Essentially a simple bar with the usual goodness, but a deeper meaning, 

Suitable for face and body. For normal to oily skin.

name: CRUST x Bettr Coffee It'd Bettr Be Beer!
Crystal Deodorant Stone
description:
Bamboo Straw Girl's bestselling deodorant is easy to use, store and take travelling! The stone is supplied in a pouch made from offcut fabrics, supporting a community of seamstresses in a seaside village with a second stream of income.

Usage: Run a bit of the stone under a tap and rub onto any area where you want to prevent body odour - yes, it will work on armpits and feet!

Regular commercial deodorants and antiperspirants contain harmful chemicals! Avoid these nasties with deodorant stones!

How does the deo stone work? The stone targets the bacteria on the skin surface, which is what causes smells. Using the stone will not clog your pores or leave any residue or by-product. It will not stain clothing. The stone deodorises by acting on the bacteria. It is not an antiperspirant! Sweating is natural and important!

What is the stone made of? The stones are made using natural mineral salts, and the main ingredient is potassium alum. Potassium alum it is not an antiperspirant and products containing it do not reduce sweat production.

It is not the same as Aluminium Chloride and Aluminium Chlorohydrate, which are commonly found in conventional antiperspirants and which people want to avoid! (Read more below)*

How long will one block last? It can last for a year or more, depending on usage!

What is the difference between potassium alum and Aluminium Chloride and Aluminium Chlorohydrate?

Aluminium Chloride and Aluminium Chlorohydrate react with peptides and amino acids in the skin to form a gel which then blocks sweat ducts and glands, preventing perspiration. This is why they are used as antiperspirants in conventional deodorants. They have a small molecular mass (usually 250-350 Daltons) which means that they can readily penetrate the skin, entering the body.

Potassium alum has a much larger molecule (approx 480 Daltons) which is too large to be absorbed through the skin. Instead of forming a gel which prevents perspiration, potassium alum sits on the surface of the skin. It is anti-bacterial and does not allow the bacteria responsible for causing bad odours to multiply."

Dead Sea Celtic Salt Bar
description:
Specially formulated for psoriasis warriors even though it can be used for all skin types (except eczema skin that may not respond well to exfoliation)

With ingredients that are specially chosen to be friendly for the psoriasis skin, including avocado oil, apricot kernel oil, dead sea clay, bentonite clay, turmeric and celtic sea salt. This bar also contains free-flowing organic coconut oil that further helps to hold moisture for the skin.

Properties of ingredients chosen:
Dead Sea Clay
Anti-inflammatory, Detoxifying
Collagen-Boosting, Hydrating
Exfoliating, Rejuvenating

Bentonite Clay
Remove impurities and toxins through adsorption
Anti-bacterial
Anti-inflammatory

Turmeric
Anti-inflammatory
May reduce PhK, a protein responsible for overproduction of skin cells.
Enhance skin barrier functions 

Celtic Sea Salt
Gentle exfoliation to remove skin buildup to increase effectiveness of hydration and treatment

Avocado oil
Emollient for hydration
Anti-inflammatory,
Antioxidant, Vitamin E

Organic coconut oil
Soften psoriasis scales
Natural moisturiser

*This bar helps to relieve some psoriasis symptoms but does not cure the condition. It works best as a complimentary skincare routine and should not replace any treatment.

**Do note that the bars for sale have been well cured for more than a month and over time, the colours no longer look as vibrant as what you see in the pictures when they were first crafted. But they have become even more lovely bars to enjoy.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.
As the bar contains sea salt, please handle the bar gently and lather in your hands before applying to the face instead of rubbing it directly.

For body, choose to rub on skin lightly in circular motion for a gentle massage and exfoliation twice a week and for rest of days, lather in hand for shower.

On hot days, you can choose to leave lather on skin and feel a cool rush before rinsing off.

Skin Types:
Formulated for Psoriasis warriors but suitable for all skin types. except eczema-prone skin areas.

name: Dissolve [Dishwash Powder] Waterless Format!
description:
We bring you Bare Necessities Dish Wash Powder, Dissolve! Rather than buying heavy containers full of water, get only the active ingredients and mix it at home!
Embracing the strength of Reetha with citrus-y grapefruit fragrance, this comes together to make an extremely safe, effective and powerful dishwasher!

Benefits:
Lower carbon footprint: we are not transporting heavy containers full of 90% water!
Completely compostable packaging: We even use Vegetable Ink (which makes even the writing on the packaging compostable!)
Plant-based and earth-friendly ingredients: Good for you, your children, and groundwater!
Refreshing fragrances: You will definitely not miss the traditional and conventional that come with loads of ingredients we can't pronounce
100% effective: A luxurious lather that effectively removes surface oil, dirt, and bacteria without stripping or drying sensitive skin
PVA can be controversial: We chose not to move forward with this because PVA can break down into smaller plastics contaminating groundwater. PVA stands for Polyvinyl Alcohol; a synthetic plastic polymer that is often used to make thin layers of plastic wrapping and lining, like the wrapping of dishwashers. PVA is a type of plastic, and while it is designed to dissolve, it doesn’t necessarily disappear. The study suggests that over 75% of PVA persists in our waterways and our soil after it dissolves in laundry and dish washing machines, flows through wastewater and ultimately back into our environment.
Finally, save money, space, water and compost! 

Size: 16 g refill pack [Makes 250ml liquid dishwash]

Shelf life: Use within 12 months of manufacture. Store in a cool, dry place

Directions for use:
1 sachet for 250ml
1. Fill dispenser with 250ml warm water 
2. Add the Bare dishwash powder in the water
3. Stir well with the help of a dispenser pipe
4. Close the lid and wait for it to completely dissolve
5. Voila! Your product is ready to use in 15 minutes
6.Use the dispenser to pump the solution into the coconut scrubbie, or right into the dish or hand! 

Some Bare tips and tricks:
You only need one push down on your dispenser for an amazing outcome! This can last you for 100+ washes! 
If needed, you can add the solution to the dish directly, and scrub away! 


Ingredients: Sodium Cocoyl Isethionate, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Acacia senegal gum, Xanthan gum, Gluconolactone, Sodium benzoate, Citrus paradisi (Grapefruit) essential oil, Citrus sinensis (Sweet Orange) Essential Oil,, Citrus aurantium (Neroli) essential oil, Citrus Grandis (Grapefruit) Extract, Tartaric acid, Sapindus Mukorossi Peel (Soapberry) Extract.

All ingredients are plant-derived, earth-friendly, and safe for groundwater!
Caution: Keep out of reach of children. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with water and seek immediate medical assistance.
brand_name: Bare Necessities Zero Waste Solutions Pvt. Ltd.

name: Down to Earth Shampoo Bar (Natural, Vegan)
description:
Mighty yet humble, “flax” that beautiful hair with the combination of flaxseed, hemp and moringa! Yup, if you were looking for an earthy protein shake for your hair, we got you!

Promotes healthy hair by strengthening roots
Loaded with protein and omega 3, 6 and 9 fatty acids
Helps prevent breakage and anti-frizz

Did you know that moringa is loaded with nutrients such as Vitamins A, B, C & E, Iron, Zinc and Essential Amino Acids which are very valuable to the hair. This herb is rich in chlorophyll, complete amino-acids, and antioxidants, all of which are responsible for nourishing your hair.

Completely natural, safe and biodegradable ingredients that come together to ensure treatment of dry and damaged hair while giving it that shine and softness! A plant-based formulation that is safe for you and the environment!

All this comes with an earthy scent with a hint of fresh citrus from lemongrass!

Our products derive their colour and scent from natural ingredients and are without any added or artificial colours. The natural colour & scent may change over time but it doesn’t affect the efficacy of the product

Country of Origin: India

How To Use: Massage gently onto wet hair and scalp, rinse thoroughly. Each bar gives you 30-50 washes (depending on hair thickness and length).

End of Life: Once done, you can compost the packaging of the shampoo bar!

name:
endota Organics
Balancing Face Moisturiser
description: If you’ve ever struggled to strike the ideal balance when dealing with oily skin, you’ll find it here. Calling on some of nature’s most effective antioxidants – grapeseed and aloe vera – we’ve developed this lightweight, balancing facial moisturiser to soothe skin that’s prone to acne, redness or inflammation. Without losing any of the moisture that leaves you glowing.

name:
endota Organics
Breast Oil
description: Made sustainably from oils derived from the world around us, endota Organic breast oil can smoothen the skin around your breast area and leave your chest looking its best – while promoting lymphatic drainage and better circulation. Use it to encourage regular breast health. And be sure to seek further medical advice if you notice any changes (beyond softer, revitalised skin).

name:
endota Organics
Coffee & Coconut Resurfacing Polish
description: Use this creamy, granulated polish once or twice a week, from head to toe. It will stimulate circulation and resurface your skin – while the caffeine delivers its firming, invigorating benefits. You’ll be left with skin that feels smooth, looks fresh and firm and glows from this natural nourishment.

name:
endota Organics
Daily Renewal Exfoliant
description: A daily polish that’s sure to set your skin aglow. When skin loses its lustre, our dual-action exfoliant is designed to gently renew skin. Its creamy formulation is bursting with antioxidants, vitamin-rich botanicals Davidson plum and amla berry, both bio-active native Australian ingredients that help defend against premature ageing. An added blend of natural bamboo and jojoba beads assists in removing impurities to reveal a smoother, more luminous-looking complexion.

name:
endota Organics
Deep Hydration Moisturiser
description: Made with an abundance of natural ingredients and oils – including avocado, amla berry grapeseed and organic rosehip oil – this moisturiser will leave your skin feeling hydrated and full of life. Think more elasticity, more luminosity, more of that naturally-dewy appearance, and 45% more hydration when used twice daily for 12 weeks.

name:
endota Organics
Hydrating Lip Balm
description: Healthy and hydrated lips don’t just make for a more radiant smile. They leave you feeling great too. Our Hydrating Lip Balm has been clinically-formulated using natural ingredients to keep the delicate skin on your lips locked with moisture. Cocoa butter, calendula and vitamin E work together to offer healthy hydration, while cooling peppermint oil provides a splash of freshness.

name:
endota Organics
Intense Moisture Mask
description: There’s a whole list of active botanicals and nourishing natural ingredients behind your luminosity – including omegas 3 and 6 and Vitamins C and E. All working together to give your skin the deeply-hydrating love it deserves, while staying naturally free from over 50 toxins you might find in other products. Use it overnight and you’ll awake to super-soft, glowing skin – with hydration levels increasing by 32%.

name:
endota Organics
Intimate Wash
description: It’s a sensitive, foaming wash that utilises the gentle effects of calendula, aloe vera and oats to wash away bacteria without leading to irritation. At the same time, apple cider vinegar maintains the ideal pH balance – while Rosa essential oil helps to elevate self-care at its most intimate.

name:
endota Organics
Lemon Peel & Sage Body Cleanser
description: Wake your whole body up to what’s possible in a new day, with this energising, revitalising all-over body wash. Infused with sage and the peel of lemon aspen – a native Australian citrus – you’ll be free to bask in the tangy fragrance, while your skin soaks up the naturally refreshing qualities. At the same time, grapeseed oil and aloe vera soothe and soften – so you feel replenished inside and out.

name:
endota Organics
Signature Blend Hand & Body Lotion
description: Notes of bergamot and ylang ylang will immediately relieve tension and take you back to endota spa. They’re mixed with naturally-sourced, and sublimely-nourishing shea butter – so your skin feels deeply hydrated and wrapped in a relaxing aroma. Relaxation mode is on.

name:
endota Organics
Vitamin Treatment Oil
description: Combining deeply-hydrating and rejuvenating essential oils – including argan, avocado and rosehip – this potent blend nourishes your skin the way a revitalising facial does. It’s light on the skin but big on the ways it moisturises and reduces the signs of ageing. Free from chemicals and toxins – and sustainably-packaged too. A treatment that’s good for your skin and the earth all at once.

name:
endota Organics Nurture
Gentle Baby Lotion
description: Keep baby’s skin hydrated and happy with this gentle, certified natural and 100% non-toxic lotion. Dermatologically tested and carefully formulated, this delicate lotion will nourish and restore moisture to even the most sensitive newborn skin. It’s enriched with organic oat and calendula to soothe skin without irritation and infused with the aromas of lavender and chamomile, so mum and bub can enjoy a moment of calm.

name:
endota Organics Nurture
Gentle Bath & Body Wash
description: This gentle 3-in-1 product is perfect for bathtime with bub. This soap-free and non-toxic shampoo, body wash and bubble bath will cleanse and condition their delicate skin and hair, while keeping skin hydrated and happy. Enriched with certified organic ingredients like oat, chamomile and lavender, it will help soothe even the most sensitive newborn skin and calm their senses for a relaxing bathtime ritual. Dermatologically tested and pH balanced, you can relax knowing you’re nourishing their skin without any nasties.

name:
endota Organics Nurture
Moisture Rich Belly Butter
description: Soothe itchy, dry and stretched skin with this COSMOS certified organic belly butter. Naturally hydrating and nourishing for pregnant bellies, it’s enriched with shea and cocoa butter and rosehip and argan oils for luxuriously soft and supple skin.

name:
endota Organics Nurture
Nourishing Nipple Balm

endota Organics Nurture 
Hydrating Belly Oil

endota Organics Nurture 
Protecting Barrier Balm

Simply spray it all over your linen to create a cosy, calming ambience – adding a special touch to your bedtime ritual.

name: endota Organics Purifying Cleansing Gel

At the same time, calendula soothes your skin and maintains vital moisture. Your complexion will feel clearer, calmer and altogether more pure. It’s all sustainably sourced and packaged – making for a clear conscience as well.

Genie in a bottle [Zero Waste Multi-Surface Cleaner] Waterless Format!
description:
You asked, we delivered! Introducing Bare Necessities Multi-Surface Cleaner Powder, Genie in a Bottle! Just like the name suggests, this magical, earth-friendly formulation gives you the 10% active ingredients to tackle various surfaces and keep your homes clean!

Pay for only the 10% active ingredients and not the huge plastic containers with 90% water!

Fresh, fruity and floral scents along with other earth & groundwater friendly ingredients to remove grime, dirt and unwanted odors!

Suited for:

Kitchen countertops, glass windows, photo frames, the inside of ovens, laminate surfaces, granite - Spray the solution and clean

Bathroom fixtures, grease stains, water stains, Tough stains - Spray the solution and leave it for 1-2 mins and clean

Not suited for: Hardwood floors

Benefits:

Lower carbon footprint: we are not transporting heavy containers full of 90% water!
Completely compostable packaging: We even use Vegetable Ink (which makes even the writing on the packaging compostable!)
Plant-based and earth-friendly ingredients: Good for you, your children, and groundwater!
Refreshing fragrances: You will definitely not miss the traditional and conventional that come with loads of ingredients we can't pronounce
100% effective: A powerful solution that effectively removes surface oil, dirt, bacteria from a variety of surfaces effectively!
PVA can be controversial: We chose not to move forward with this because PVA can breakdown into smaller plastics contaminating groundwater. PVA stands for Polyvinyl Alcohol ; a synthetic plastic polymer that is often used to make thin layers of plastic wrapping and lining, like the wrapping of dishwashers. PVA is a type of plastic, and while it is designed to dissolve, it doesn’t necessarily disappear. The study suggests that over 75% of PVA persists in our waterways and our soil after it dissolves in laundry and dish washing machines, flows through wastewater and ultimately back into our environment.
Finally, save money, space, water and compost! 

Size: 5g refill pack [Makes 250ml liquid handwash]

Shelf life: Use within 12 months of manufacture. Store in a cool, dry place
1 sachet for 250ml

Directions for use:
1. Fill dispenser with warm water upto the mark
2. Add the Bare multisurface powder in the water
3. Stir well with the help of a dispenser pipe
4. Close the lid and wait for it to completely dissolve
5. Voila! Your product is ready to use in 15 minutes
6.Use the dispenser to spray the solution on all kinds of surfaces!

Some Bare tips and tricks:
You only need one push down on your dispenser for an amazing outcome! This can last you for 100+ washes! 

Ingredients: Sodium bicarbonate, Tartaric acid, Sodium citrate, Gluconolactone, Sodium benzoate, Sodium Cocoyl Isethionate, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate,Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Extract, Citrus Paradisi (Grapefruit) essential oil, Cananga Odorata (Ylang ylang) essential oil, Sapindus Mukorossi Peel (Soapberry) Extract. 

All ingredients are plant-derived, earth-friendly, and safe for groundwater!

Caution: Keep out of reach of children. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with water and seek immediate medical assistance. For external use only. 

Country of Origin: Made in India (many others are imported or come in plastic!)

name: Ginger Bliss
description:
A perfect "mummy shower" postpartum confinement gift as she celebrates the birth of her new baby. PAMPER the new mummy with the self care she TOTALLY needs and deserves.

A beautiful bar too for all ginger lovers.

Formulated with "Triple Ginger" - Pure Young Ginger Juice, Grated Ginger, Organic Ginger Powder, Cocoa Butter and Maple Syrup. Unscented. The modern day ginger bath for confinement mummies that comes unscented so the mummies can breastfeed their babies with total peace of mind. 

Besides ginger, the bar contains cocoa butter which is known for its ability penetrate into deeper layers of the skin dermis to aid with skin repair and minimising of stretch marks. Though unscented, you can catch a whiff of light chocolate scent because of the unrefined cocoa butter. The bar also contains maple syrup which is said to help with lightening of dark spots like stretch mark and pigmentation in addition to tightening of the skin. Not only that, maple syrup helps to add more luxurious bubbles to let the mummy fully wind down during her precious me-time during the showers.

Cos when a baby is born, so is a mother. And every mother deserves the same love and care after her bundle of joy is delivered.

Usage:
Daily use on body.

Skin Types:
All skin types

name: Lavender Levitate Bath Salts [Natural Self-care]
description:
A simple way to treat yourself after a long, hard day. This blend has been designed to help you relax, draw out toxins, lower stress and balance your natural pH levels. The rose petals have a refreshing, uplifting scent ideal for all skin types, while the lemongrass essential oil is a calming, antidepressant, anti-inflammatory, and antiseptic agent. A feel good solution for our bodies, minds, souls and planet 

Ingredients: Magnesium sulphate (Epsom salt), Sodium chloride, Cocos nucifera (Coconut) oil, Lavandula angustifolia (Lavender) essential oil, Lavender buds

How To Use: Bath tub: Add 5-6 spoonfuls to your warm water bath
Bucket bath: Add 2-3 spoonfuls to your bucket of warm water
Soak your feet: Add 1-2 spoonfuls to your bucket of warm water
Relax!

End of Life: 
Once done, there are many ways to ensure the jar doesn’t go waste
Reuse the glass jar for other household items or DIY ideas
Repurpose the glass jar as beautiful vases or household item storage
Refill more Bare goodies using our refill stations or returning the jars to us
Return the glass jars to Bare Necessities for further discounts and generate less waste!
Recycle the glass jar at your nearest dry waste centers

Country of Origin: India
brand_name: Bare Necessities Zero Waste Solutions Pvt. Ltd.

name: Lavender Oatmeal
description:
Our top selling bar with a strong following, this bar combines a nourishing 5 oil-blend with the goodness of two all-time favourite soap ingredients - organic oatmeal and the soothing Lavender essential oil. Suitable for all ages and skin type, including sensitive skin and children.

The coconut oil cleanses naturally while avocado and olive oil hydrates and nourishes the skin with vitamins and antioxidant. Castor oil works up a luxurious lather for you without any artificial additive. The organic oatmeal tops off a relaxing shower with the gentle exfoliation it provides, coupled with the soothing Lavender scent.
​
Handmade, hand-poured and hand-cut, all in Singapore. Every piece is unique and comes with a sustainable message.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.

Skin Types:
All skin types especially very dry and sensitive skin.

name: Love is in the (h)air Conditioner Bar [Natural, Vegan, Nutrient-rich]
description:
The perfect soulmate for your hair, we promise you’ll fall deeply in love, with its deep conditioning ways, pretty much as good as a hair spa, we’d say! 

Much needed nourishment for your hair 
Rich in nutrients to promote hair strength and elasticity 
Rich in biotin to strengthen hair follicles 
A natural anti-oxidant 

Did you know that Seabuckthorn Oil, often referred to as the holy fruit of the Himalayas is super rich in Vitamins A, B, C, E, & K and promotes hair strength and elasticity. 

Completely natural, safe and biodegradable ingredients that come together to ensure treatment of dry and damaged hair while giving it that shine and softness! A plant-based formulation that is safe for you and the environment! 

All this comes with an uplifting fragrance of rosemary, lemongrass and basil! This blend of essential oil is used traditionally to promote hair growth and reduce hair loss and are sourced locally

Country of Origin: India

Ingredients: Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Cetyl Alcohol, Cocoa Butter, Seabuckthorn Oil, Cetostearyl Alcohol, Vitamin B5, Vitamin E, Rosemary Essential Oil, Lemongrass Essential Oil, Basil Essential Oil, Gluconolactone & Sodium benzoate (ECOCERT Approved) 

How To Use: Massage gently onto wet hair. Leave conditioner on hair for 1-2 minutes for maximum effectiveness. Rinse thoroughly. ​​Each bar gives you 30-50 washes (depending on hair thickness and length). 

End of Life: Once done, you can compost the packaging of the shampoo bar!
brand_name: Bare Necessities Zero Waste Solutions Pvt. Ltd.

name: Love Luna Period Panties Bikini Brief - Moderate Absorbency
description:
Our classic cut Bikini Brief by Love Luna is the perfect everyday option. Made from sleek microfibre with a cute lace trim, it looks just like normal underwear!

Featuring a super comfy inbuilt pad with four layer protection: Soft cotton lining, absorbent & breathable padding, a waterproof layer & a sleek microfibre outer layer. Measuring only 3mm in thickness for discreet everyday wear.

  • Absorbs 10-15ml (2-3 regular tampons)
  • Coverage:

    •  

    Size

    Sizing Table:

    SIZE WAIST (CM) HIPS (CM)
    8-10 65 93
    10-12 70 98
    12-14 75 103
    14-16 80 108
    Compare size with other brands of period underwear
      Materials & Care

      Materials:

      • Outer: Nylon/Elastane
        Lining: Cotton/Elastane
        Padding: Polyester/Viscose/Elastane (Exclusive of trims)
      • Designed in Australia

      1. Soft Cotton Lining: On the inside closest to your skin (Read: breathable for your vagina)
      2. Absorbent Padding: Breathable 2x way stretch padding to absorb the spills
      3. Waterproof layer: The star of the show! Guarding you against any accidental leaks, protecting your sheets, clothing & preventing awkward accidents
      4. Sleek Microfibre: This is what you're seeing on the outside, and is also the same fabric as our Midi Brief

      Care Instructions:

      • Wash before wear. Cold delicate machine wash with like colours. Do not add softener. Do not soak. Do not bleach. Do not tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean. Line dry.

name: Love Luna Period Panties Teen Bikini
description:
Our Teens First Period Bikini briefs are specifically designed to fit tweens and teens, made in junior sizes for younger growing bodies. FIRST by Love Luna period briefs have 4 layers of absorbency and protection to guard against life's annoying and sometimes embarrassing situations.

  • Absorbs 10-15ml (2-3 regular tampons)
  • Coverage:

    •

    Measurements:

    • Junior Sizing Guide

      SIZE WAIST (CM)
      6-8 57-59
      8-10 59-61
      10-12 61-63
      12-14 63-66
      14-16 66-69
    Material & Care

    Materials:

    • Outer: 90% BCI Cotton, 10% Elastane
      Gusset: 100% Cotton
      Padding: 80% Cotton, 20% Polyester (Exclusive of trims)
    • Designed in Australia

    1. Soft Cotton Lining: On the inside closest to your skin (Read: breathable for your vagina)
    2. Absorbent Padding: Breathable 2x way stretch padding to absorb the spills
    3. Waterproof layer: The star of the show! Guarding you against any accidental leaks, protecting your sheets, clothing & preventing awkward accidents
    4. Sleek Microfibre: This is what you're seeing on the outside, and is also the same fabric as our Bikini Brief

    Care Instructions:

    • Wash before wear. Cold delicate machine wash with like colours. Do not add softener. Do not soak. Do not bleach. Do not tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean. Line dry.

name: Lychee & Orange Flower
description:
Everybody loves lychee for its tropical flora fragrance and lusciousness. The Lychee from the orchards at Vatovavy-Fitovinany is known for its outstanding quality.
Hand-picked by our farmers when the lychees are ripe on the trees, these fully grown and sunbathed lychees offer their best and fullest flavor.
In the kitchen, our team, formed by local Malagasy village ladies, carefully peel, deseed, and prepare the fruits to obtain a velvety texture. To finish, Brigitte enchanted it with a touch of orange blossom.
Voila, a jam of great originality! Absolutely irresistible!

Pair: Croissant, baguette, duck confit, martini

name: Marshmallow Bubblegum
description:
This soap bar is made of the traditional REAL marshmallows, not the gelatin ones that we eat these days.

Crafted with marshmallow roots - a herb that has been used for thousands of years to treat respiratory, digestive and skin conditions.⁠⁠ This sweet delight is not just a treat to our taste buds, it is an amazing natural ingredient for our skin. Scented with the milder mint, Spearmint.
⁠⁠
Marshmallow roots contain anti-inflammatory properties that has been found in some studies to help relieve skin irritation caused by skin conditions such as eczema. ⁠⁠ In addition, some studies have found that antibacterial properties in marshmallow roots may help to speed up wound healing. In some cases, marshmallow root is even used in skincare to protect again UV radiation.

We specially formulated this bar to add to our eczema friendly series so that friends with eczema who is OK with essential oil can enjoy a fun bar that is good for their skin too.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.

Skin Types:
All skin types including dry, sensitive, eczema-prone skin.

name: Mason & Co x Bare Lip Balm
description:
Lip smackingly good. Made from all natural ingredients, the Cocoa Butter Lip Balm has been specially formulated with vitamins and essential fatty acids to nourish, condition and soften lips. Vegan soy seals in hydration, while the cocoa butter marks for a delicious chocolatey flavour! P.S. We truly believe in the power of collaborations and Mason & Co. is a beautiful social enterprise which believes in the same. Read more here about their enterprise and why we support one another!

Great for everyday maintenance - for daily maintenance, light and non-greasy; great for summer months! 

A lip balm that will last you 1+ years! 

Country of Origin: India

Ingredients: Cocoa butter | Shea butter | Organic almond oil | Organic coconut oil | Vegan soy wax | Chocolate essence
brand_name: Bare Necessities Zero Waste Solutions Pvt. Ltd.

name: Matcha Azuki
description:
GLOW NATURALLY with a natural bar every shower.

Matcha Azuki soap with Camellia, scented with Lemon Eucalyptus. A bar filled with simple goodness known to noblewomen since hundreds of years ago. 
​
Azuki bean powder had been used for hundreds of years in Japanese skincare regime to rejuvenate and brighten the skin. It is rich in saponin and provides deep cleansing and exfoliation to remove dead skin cell, unclog pores, which explains why Japanese noblewomen had been using it since 18th century to improve circulation for a natural glow.⁠

Not forgetting the star ingredient - MATCHA! Matcha is a beautiful natural ingredient that is suitable for all skin types. Not only is it said to help fight signs of aging, matcha is gentle enough even for the young skin!⁠ Possibly helpful for pre-teens or teens pounded with acne woes. With its anti-inflammatory properties, it reduces redness of the skin, while its tannin content is said to help address over production of oil and tighten pores.⁠
⁠
And the story doesn't end here. Camellia oil which is believed as one of the beauty secrets of Geishas! Rich with antioxidant and Vitamin E, Camellia oil is also non comedogenic making it suitable even for oily skin. It is known to absorb quickly and deeply into the skin, promoting skin health.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.

Skin Types:
All skin types.

name: Medium Standup Storage Bag
description:
Go ahead and use this MOST VERSATILE size endlessly for just anything you can think of for your Kitchen & Beyond keeping your life neat & organised. 

PERFECT FOR: Packing lunches on the go, keeps various foods fresh, spill proof sauces/soups, meal-prep, marinades, pantry lineup, pack travel supplies (like toiletries, cosmetics, medicines), keep your belongings safe and the perfect gift for all occasions.

MADE OF: 100% pure platinum food grade silicone. Contains 0% plastic and other harmful substances like BPA, BPS, PVC, Latex, Lead, Phthalates etc.

TEMPERATURE RANGE:  Designed to withstand temperature range of-60C up to +220C making them perfectly safe for use in Microwave or Freezer.

STANDUP FLAT BOTTOM: Designed to Stand allowing for liquid stuff to be poured in and taken out conveniently avoiding the hassles of spills.

LEAKPROOF, EASY TO OPEN & CLOSE: Designed with a wide and thick opening with superior sealing performance making them leakproof, hence, perfect fresh-keeping effect. 

WATERPROOF: Our bags are 100% waterproof. Whether exposed to rain or mistakenly fall in swimming pool or get wet; the contents will always remain dry. 

CONVENIENT: Super convenient to store in comparison to the bulky glass or toxic plastic containers. Organize them by writing/drawing with markers

SAVE COST SAVE PLANET & SAVE YOUR HEALTH: ONE Reusable UNPLASTIK bag can replace up to 3000 single-use plastics. No worry of toxic chemicals leaching into your food.

DIMENSIONS: 22*15.8*8.7cm; Capacity - 1300ml/44 fl.oz

SHIPPING: All orders are shipped in 24 hours and delivered within 3-4 business days.

name: Modibodi Period Panties Classic Bikini - Heavy Absorbency
description:
BACK IN STOCK!
Take a look at our alternative period panties here. 

Description:
The signature Classic Bikini is the perfect style for every day AND night in our Heavy-Overnight absorbency. With a longer secured gusset that has protection up to the back waist band, these undies will keep you dry and comfy with the extra protection giving you support through the night.
This absorbency is perfect for those in serious pelvic floor training, incontinence or for heavy periods with overnight protection to keep your sheets stain free!  

Material: Bamboo
Care:  Hand wash or light cold machine wash, hang to dry, no fabric softeners or strong detergents eg. stain removers
Dimensions: Heavy lining holds up to 20ml (3-4 tampons or 4 tsp)
Not sure which menstrual product to use?
Check out our blog post "Take Control of Your Periods"

Modibodi Period Underwear Classic Bikini - MAXI-24Hrs Absorbency
description:
This signature Classic Bikini combines everyday comfort with our ultimate Maxi-24hrs protection for those with very heavy periods, frequent bladder leaks or the need for up to 24 hours* of wear. Featuring our patent-pending absorbent technology all the way from the front to the back waistband (we've got front and back bleeders covered), this is your must-have bikini for a stress-free sleep - and no more messy sheets!

MAXI-24HRS

Flow: 50ml =  10 tampons, or 10 teaspoons 
For: A very heavy flow or a style you can wear for up to 24hrs* 
Feels: Slim, light and dry for the whole day and night 
Impact: Eliminate disposables, better for your body & the planet! 
* Patent-pending Maxi-24hrs technology has been tested to hold 50ml per day, the average woman loses 2 to 3 tablespoons or 30-50ml of blood over 5 days
Size

Measurements:

  • Click here for sizing chart
  • Sits on Hip, High Leg
  • Heavy lining holds up to 20ml (3-4 tampons or 4 tsp)
  • Modibodi garments fit and wear like regular underwear
Material & Care

Material:

  • Outer - Bamboo & Spandex
  • Liner - Merino Wool, Polyester, Polyamide
  • Designed in Australia

Care Instructions:

  • Hand wash or light cold machine wash, hang to dry, no fabric softeners or strong detergents eg. stain removers

name: Modibodi Recycled Swimwear Bikini Brief
description:
Never miss a pool party again in these Swimwear Bikini Briefs, made from an innovative new recycled fabric. Featuring a hi-cut leg and fast-drying absorbent lining, it’s the perfect leak-proof pair to hit the beach – without fear of leaks. Made from an innovative NEW recycled fabric that is chlorine-resistant and UV50+ rated.

LIGHT-MODERATE

Flow: 10ml = 2 tampons or 1-2 teaspoons
For: Spotting, discharge, light to moderate flow or light bladder leaks
Feels: Like your favourite swimmers – yet with a confidence boost
Impact: Less tampons on their way to landfill or clogging the oceans

Size

Measurements:

  • Click here for sizing chart
  • Flow: 10ml = 2 tampons or 1-2 teaspoons
Material & Care

Material:

  • Outer - 82% Pre-consumer Recycled Nylon 18% Spandex
  • Lining - 84% Pre-consumer Recycled Nylon 16% Spandex
  • Gusset - 100% Polyester

Care Instructions:

  • Rinse before then gently cold machine wash, hang to dry...and repeat. (No fabric softeners or stain removers please)

name: OASIS Room and Linen Mist
description:
Fresh Linen

Who can resist the crisp clean scent of freshly washed linens drying out under the sun? Featuring notes of cotton and sweet powdery musk, this room and linen spray will instantly chase away any undesired odours and infuse that elegant powdery touch to your garments and room. Mist over your pillow to lull yourself into a relaxing sleep. After all, you deserve to be swathed in layers and layers of cottony clouds in your beauty rest don’t you think?

Notes:

Cotton Flower, Lily-of-the-Valley, Freesia, Musk, Vanilla.

Iris Forest

The delightful union of enlivening White Iris balanced with hints of green and aromatic woody notes. Invoke creative energy into any space and let the buttery soft scent work its magic. 

Notes: 

Irises, Violets, Warm Wood, Watery pear, Musk and Rose.

Tea & Musk

Embrace the harmony of this mist that blends floral island blossoms and powdery musk with the purity of distilled green tea leaves. Spray this over your covers, rugs or even use this as a perfume - the choices are endless. 

Notes:

Bergamot, Musk, Lemon zest, Island blossoms and Tea Leaves.

 

What is the International Fragrance Association (IFRA)?

The International Fragrance Association (IFRA) is the

official self-regulatory representative body of the fragrance industry worldwide. Founded in 1973, IFRA publishes a list of safe usage standards for fragrance materials, limiting or prohibiting the use of ingredients, based on the findings of the Research Institute of Fragrance Materials, which gathers data regarding the safety of fragrance materials. In 2020, the association also started to focus on sustainability in the beauty and fragrance sector. 

 Find out more about the IFRA standards through this independent link here

Directions

Spray two to three pumps throughout the immediate space or surface and refresh as needed

Ingredients

Alcohol Denat (Plant-based Perfume Alcohol), Parfum, Aqua.

name: Organic Cotton Produce Bags Combo - GOTS Certified
description:
Our Purple & Pure 100% Organic Cotton Mesh bags are lightweight and see-through, ensuring air circulation within the stored produce. Both bags come with a drawstring closure, so you could hang them up hence saving counter space. Our Purple & Pure 100% organic cotton produce drawstring bags are now available in mesh and muslin material. Both bags come with a drawstring closure, so you could hang them up hence saving counter space.

The mesh bags are lightweight and see-through, ensuring air circulation within the stored produce. The muslin is great for storing produce in the fridge, and you could also use it to store a loaf of bread or bulk bag when you visit the bakery or bulk store.



Bring these with you to the grocery store and farmers' market and never use another single-use plastic produce bag again!


Our organic cotton muslin produce bags are made from 100% cotton. They are certified organic through GOTS (Global Organic Textile Standard).


Your purchase includes:

Set of 4: Organic Mesh Produce bag - 2, Organic Muslin Produce bag -2 The sizes of the bags are 10″ x 12″. Sustainably sourced and made in India.

All bags packaged in eco-friendly boxes make a wonderful gift.



Here are 6 reasons why you should Choose Organic Produce Bags:
1. Multi-Purpose
Our mesh and muslin bags are not only for food items like fruit, vegetables, and snacks but also great for grains, beans, coffee, rice. You can even use the organic muslin bags for straining nut milks and yogurt. Our reusable multi-purpose bags can be used for so many things: toy storage, lego, cosmetics, toiletry bags, travel, laundry, accessories, and gift bags.

2. Certified Organic
100% GOTS Certified Organic Cotton: Our premium mesh and muslin produce bags are made of breathable, biodegradable natural fiber, non-toxic Our reusable produce bags are made from the finest organic cotton without the use of any harmful synthetic pesticides, or fertilizers. You can feel safe placing your bags straight into the fridge. Unlike traditional plastic, Organic bags are BPA Free and contain no Mercury, PVC or Lead. Keep your food safe from contaminants with Organic produce bags! Certified food safe. 100% Pure Certified Organic Cotton

3. Eco-Friendly & Zero Waste</li>
Eco-friendly natural unbleached biodegradable organic cotton mesh and muslin reusable produce bags are the best alternatives to single-use plastic bags. Help eliminate single-use plastic and reduce plastic pollution in our oceans, waterways, and shorelines. Help save our planet. Create zero waste and be eco-conscious. Purple & Pure bags are premium reusable natural cotton biodegradable produce bags are a simple way to reduce the use of plastic bags and make a real positive impact on our environment. The mesh allows for an easy view to see the contents inside and allows for air circulation so fruits and vegetables can breathe.

Even our packaging is 100% recycled box which makes these bags zero waste bags.

4. Machine Washable/ Easy to Clean
These reusable organic produce bags are machine washable in cold water. To increase the lifespan of the bags lay flat to dry. Dry on low heat or hang to dry.

5. Lightweight & Portable
Our bags are foldable and can be easily stored in the smallest of drawers. They are portable and their lightweight makes them easy to carry in your purse, shopping bag or backpack.

6. Durable & Convenient
Purple & Pure reusable produce bags are made of premium quality organic cotton. Our seams have been reinforced with double stitching and our double drawstring design makes closing each bag extremely easy and convenient. There are no plastic beads or metal buckles, just an instant-close drawstring.

name: Rice Milk Bar
description:
A bar specially formulated for our friends with dry skin, so they can enjoy a good daily cleansing at home without feeling the skin is tight and stretched afterwards. In fact, the skin feels refreshed, supple and smooth, making every face wash an enjoyable event.

This is one of our bars with the most amount of pre-work prior to actual soaping day. Cos every bar is made with rice milk lovingly homemade with organic brown rice, to extract the goodness with the least processing and with minimum prepackaging.

Since ancient times, people in many Asian countries have known and appreciated the beautiful effects of rice water on their skin. Many believe in their lightening, brightening properties and if you've ever washed rice, you might have also noticed first-hand how smooth your skin feels afterwards. And that is an effect we strive to replicate in our bar.

This bar boasts of not just rice milk, rice bran oil, avocado oil, shea butter and maple, all chosen specifically for their skin hydrating properties. And the best part, keeping the skin moist doesn't compromise on cleansing. The bar contains white kaolin clay which is the gentlest of all clays that helps to remove dead skin and impurities for even sensitive skin to reveal a brighter, smoother complexion.

Lightly scented with Lavender, Eucalyptus and Peppermint essential oils. This is the bar formulated for dry skin facial wash but can definitely be used too as a nourishing body soap.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.

Skin Types:
Dry skin

name: Sachi Soy Wine - 187 ML
description:
Sachi is the world's first soy-based alcoholic beverage, making waves in the new generation of drinks. Targeting the global trend towards healthier lifestyles and more conscious drinking, Sachi has been developed as a result to fill that gap. Made from Made from 100% soy whey, Sachi is a low calorie drink, containing only 70 calories per glass and packed with 80mg of antioxidants called isoflavones.

This vegan friendly and refreshing drink is lusciously sweet and full of concentrated flavour balanced by vibrant acidity, characterised by flavours of honey and apples. These notes are naturally achieved, free from additives and preservative.

Sustainably made in Singapore.

name: Singapore Shophouse Walks: Joo Chiat, Katong & Geylang book
description:
Hardcover, 210 pages, laminated 150gsm matte photo paper.
Dimensions: 22x22x3cm, ISBN 978-981-18-1608-6 This beautiful photo book leads the reader on a visual and historical journey around the east coast area of Singapore. Showcasing the Peranakan culture and architecture, stunning photos illustrate the text and clear maps show the reader where to find the most picturesque and beautiful Peranakan shophouses and terraced houses around Joo Chiat, Katong and Geylang.
Reflecting on history and present time the book would make the perfect gift for someone who is visiting or just arrived to Singapore and wants to learn more about local culture. It would also make an unforgettable keepsake for someone who is leaving the country as well as an amazing and thoughtful gift for anyone who resides in Singapore.

name: Small Standup Storage Bag
description:
Go ahead and use this SMALL size endlessly for just anything in SMALL PORTIONS you can think of for your Kitchen & Beyond keeping your life neat & organised. 

PERFECT FOR: ONE INDIVIDUAL, light leftovers, packing small portions of your/kids favourites, spill proof your sauces/soups, packing your travel supplies and essentials and the perfect gift for all occasions.

MADE OF: 100% pure platinum food grade silicone. Contains 0% plastic and other harmful substances like BPA, BPS, PVC, Latex, Lead, Phthalates etc.

TEMPERATURE RANGE: Designed to withstand temperature range of-60C up to +220C making them perfectly safe for use in Microwave or Freezer.

STANDUP FLAT BOTTOM: Designed to Stand allowing for liquid stuff to be poured in and taken out conveniently avoiding the hassles of spills.

LEAKPROOF, EASY TO OPEN & CLOSE: Designed with a wide and thick opening with superior sealing performance making them leakproof, hence, perfect fresh-keeping effect. 

WATERPROOF: Our bags are 100% waterproof. Whether exposed to rain or mistakenly fall in swimming pool or get wet; the contents will always remain dry. 

CONVENIENT: Super convenient to store in comparison to the bulky glass or toxic plastic containers. Organize them by writing/drawing with markers

SAVE COST SAVE PLANET & SAVE YOUR HEALTH: ONE Reusable UNPLASTIK bag can replace up to 3000 single-use plastics. No worry of toxic chemicals leaching into your food.

DIMENSIONS: 22*12.5*8.7cm; Capacity - 1000ml/34 fl.oz

SHIPPING: All orders are shipped in 24 hours and delivered within 3-4 business days.

name: Soak It Up
description:
A moisturizer rich in nutrients, vitamins and natural oils - soak it up for long-lasting hydration for your body and face!

This moisturizer is made with non comedogenic oils that moisturize your skin without blocking your pores. It helps to provide long lasting hydration to your skin with added nutrients that helps skin stay hydrated and nourished.

This moisturizer suits all skin types.

Rich with vitamins and minerals, apricot kernel oil is a plant-based ingredient that deeply nourishes the skin
Whether your skin type is dry, oily, or a little bit o’ both, jojoba oil can help balance out skin’s moisture levels
High in fatty acids and vitamins A, C, and E that helps nourish skin

Our products derive their colour and scent from natural ingredients and are without any added or artificial colours. The natural colour & scent may change over time and across temperatures but it doesn’t affect the efficacy of the product.

The large jar can last you 6+ months of soothening usage!

Country of Origin: India
Ingredients: Aqua, Apricot Kernel Oil,Jojoba Oil, Hemp Seed Oil, Ceteareth-20 & Cetostearyl Alcohol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Phenoxyethanol, Triethylene glycol & Neroli Essential Oil

Stir It Up [Handwash Powder]
description:
We bring you Bare Necessities Handsoap Powder, Stir it up! Like its name, only get the 10% active ingredients and mix it with water at home. Pay for only the active ingredients and not the huge plastic containers!
Embracing the strength of Reetha with citrus-y fragrance, this comes together to make an extremely safe, effective and powerful hand wash!

Benefits:
Lower carbon footprint: we are not transporting heavy containers full of 90% water!
Completely compostable packaging: We even use Vegetable Ink (which makes even the writing on the packaging compostable!)
Plant-based and earth-friendly ingredients: Good for you, your children, and groundwater!
Refreshing fragrances: You will definitely not miss the traditional and conventional that come with loads of ingredients we can't pronounce
100% effective: A luxurious lather that effectively removes surface oil, dirt, bacteria without stripping or drying sensitive skin
PVA can be controversial: We chose not to move forward with this because PVA can breakdown into smaller plastics contaminating groundwater. PVA stands for Polyvinyl Alcohol ; a synthetic plastic polymer that is often used to make thin layers of plastic wrapping and lining, like the wrapping of dishwashers. PVA is a type of plastic, and while it is designed to dissolve, it doesn’t necessarily disappear. The study suggests that over 75% of PVA persists in our waterways and our soil after it dissolves in laundry and dish washing machines, flows through wastewater and ultimately back into our environment.
Finally, save money, space, water and compost! 

Country of Origin: India
Ingredients: Sodium Cocoyl Isethionate, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Acacia senegal gum, Xanthan gum, Aniba rosaeodora (Rosewood) essential oil, Gluconolactone, Sodium benzoate, Tartaric acid, Citrus medica limonum (Lemon) essential oil, Vaccinium Myrtillus (Bilberry) Fruit Extract, Sapindus Mukorossi Peel (Soapberry) Extract.

All ingredients are plant-derived, earth-friendly, and safe for groundwater!
Caution: Keep out of reach of children. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with water and seek immediate medical assistance.

1 sachet for 250ml

Directions for use:
1. Fill dispenser with 250 ml warm water
2. Add the Bare handwash powder in the water
3. Stir well with the help of a dispenser pipe
4. Close the lid and wait for it to completely dissolve
5. Voila! Your product is ready to use in 15 minutes
6.Use the dispenser to pump the solution right into your hand! 

Some Bare tips and tricks:
You only need one push down on your dispenser for an amazing outcome! This can last you for 100+ washes! 
If needed, you can add the solution to the dish directly, and scrub away!

This gift set is perfect for anyone you know who loves gardening or appreciates eco-friendly gifts.

Product Details
– Plantable seed notebook and pencil set
– Notebook cover is printed, plantable paper embedded with Basil seeds

Materials
Recycled paper, seeds

name: TRU EARTH Eco-strip Laundry Detergent
description:
Each laundry strip packs ultra-concentrated, hypoallergenic, eco-friendly cleaning power into a tiny, pre-measured strip of liquidless laundry detergent that you just toss in the wash. Its low-sudsing formula works in all types of washing machines, including high-efficiency (HE).

The smart laundry detergent formulation effectively seeks out and dislodges dirt molecules and stains, keeping them in suspension until they are rinsed away. It makes your laundry washing chore easier, healthier, more economical, and much kinder to our planet.

Clean, green, and simple! 

  • Paraben-free
  • Phosphate-free
  • Free of added dyes
  • Free of chlorine bleach
  • Free of 1,4-dioxane, as certified by independent laboratory tests
  • Readily biodegradable in accordance with OECD 310D
  • Hypoallergenic, certified by independent dermatologists
  • Vegan: no animal-based ingredients or testing on animals by us or our ingredient suppliers
  • Manufactured in Canada

name: Turmeric Sunrise
description:
A delightfully refreshing soap bar to perk you up for a natural glow. A beautiful bar with ombre hues for lovers of Lemongrass.

This turmeric soap bar contains curcumin which is known for its anti-inflammatory ​and antioxidant properties and is said to bring out the glow and natural lustre from the skin. The same properties are also known to help soothe flares from psoriasis and other skin conditions as well as reduce acne and resulting scars.

Lemongrass contains an abundance of vitamins and minerals. Besides helping with skin glow, it is also antibacterial, antifungal, anti-inflammatory and is known to be an astringent to help minimise pores. Scent is invigorating.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.

Skin Types:
All skin types including sensitive skin.

name: Unscented Oatmeal
description:
Extra gentle with zero fragrance, this is the unscented version of our top seller, Lavender Oatmeal. So gentle it is not just excellent for very dry and sensitive skin, but safe for babies and young children too. Best for anyone who prefers to totally avoid even essential oil due to skin sensitivity.

Coconut oil cleanses while rich avocado oil provides intense hydration that leaves the skin soft, smooth and supple after showers. Castor oil helps boost bubbles for a luxurious lather without any artificial surfactant. A generous portion of organic oatmeal helps calm and soothe troubled skin while giving a natural, gentle exfoliation for a relaxing shower.

Usage:
Daily use on face and body.

Skin Types:
All skin types especially very dry and sensitive skin.

Learn how to use the Urban Composter here and join our Composting Kampung group on Facebook.

name: V-Planet Mini Bites (V-Dog)
description:
V-Planet kibble is a premium vegan dog food made in Canada with high-quality, 100% plant-powered ingredients. V-planet's complete and balanced AAFCO formula is made with yummy, nourishing, non-GMO ingredients including peas, lentils, and quinoa and is always free from allergens and fillers like corn, wheat, and soy. V-planet is ideal for all adult dogs, including pups who suffer from food allergies or sensitivities.

V-planet's sister company, v-dog food, is a family owned and operated business out of California, making plant-powered products for dogs since 2005 in the USA.

Made in Canada
Formulated by experts & meets all AAFCO standards for adult dog nutrition
Never any wheat, corn, soy, animal products, factory farming, by products, fake stuff or fillers
Available in both "regular" and "mini bites" kibble
Ingredients you can actually pronounce

Dried Peas, Ground Oats, Pea Protein, Ground Brown Rice, Potato Protein, Rapeseed Oil (Preserved with Mixed Tocopherols), Brewers Dried Yeast, Dried Alfalfa Meal, Natural Vegetable Flavors, Ground Flaxseed, Calcium Carbonate, Calcium Phosphate, Dried Lentils, Ground Quinoa Seeds, Salt, Potassium Chloride, Choline Chloride, Taurine, Dried Chicory Root, Dried Carrots, DL-Methionine, Dried Blueberries, Vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin Supplement, Vitamin A Supplement, D-Calcium Pantothenate, Thiamine Mononitrate, Riboflavin Supplement, Beta Carotene, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Vitamin D Supplement, Folic Acid, Biotin), Minerals (Copper Sulfate, Calcium Iodate, Iron Sulfate, Manganous Oxide, Zinc Oxide, Selenium Yeast, Copper Proteinate, Iron Proteinate, Zinc Proteinate, Manganese Proteinate), Dried Spinach, Dried Apples, Dried Sweet Potatoes, Dried Cranberries, L-Ascorbyl-2-Polyphosphate (Source of Vitamin C Activity), Yucca Schidigera Extract, L-Carnitine, Rosemary Extract.

Guaranteed Analysis

Protein Minimum 24%
Crude Fiber Maximum 5%
Crude Fat Minimum 10%
Moisture Maximum 10%
Calculated at 330kcal/100g

Feeding Guidelines:

Weight of Dog / Grams per Day

up to 2.3 kg / up to 71 g
2.3-4.5 kg / 71-106 g
4.5-6.8 kg / 106-159 g
6.8-9.1 kg / 159-186 g
9.1-11.3 kg / 186-212 g
11.3-13.6 kg / 212-247 g
13.6-181 kg / 247-301 g
18.1-22.7 kg / 301-355 g
22.7-27.2 kg / 355-409 g
For every 2.2 kg of body weight over 27.2 kg, add an additional 27 grams of product per day

Veterinarian Approved

Dogs can be healthy and in fact, thrive on a vegetarian or vegan diet, as long as all necessary nutrient requirements are met. Dogs are biologically omnivorous, but can adapt well to a plant-based diet which meets all their nutritional needs. It's important that the food be digested easily as well as have good palatability. One of the most common ailments in dogs is skin allergies, which may sometimes be due to food allergy. Much of the time a dog has a food allergy it is to a meat protein such as beef, chicken, or one of the other common meat sources. Vegetarian diets may bring these food allergic dogs relief from the

name: YumGrubs - Garden Paté (200g)
description:
What's new at the pet food aisle? Introducing YumGrubs – A revolutionary and nutritionally complete wet pet food that is made from 100% single source protein for dogs. YumGrubs has hypoallergenic properties and is also filler free, gluten free, nut free, soy free, commercial palatant free, contains no added flavors or preservatives making it safe for all dogs.

YumGrubs is sold in single-use, airtight pouches. When you open the bag, your nostrils will be greeted by a pleasant mix of earth and forest smells, not the typical all-too-familiar dog food odor! For starters, YumGrubs comes in a single flavour, our flagship Farmer’s Garden Pate, that even the pickiest canine palate will enjoy – and in our humble opinion, taste better than any other commercial wet pet food on the market. 

What’s more, YumGrubs is nutritionally complete, containing all of the nutrients that your dog needs to stay healthy. No need for special food bowls, or supplements. It’s convenient, high-quality pet care from a company that understands what dogs need to maintain optimal health and vitality.

Key Ingredients
Hermetia Illucens, Potatoes, Pumpkins, Carrots, Spinach, Seaweed, Rosemary, Turmeric, Fenugreek, Coriander, Agar, Guar Gum, Sunflower Oil.

description: 300mL per bottle. Yuzu is a little citrus fruit that some describe as a mashup of grapefruit, lemon and mandarin. Light, sweet and zesty, this makes for a refreshing taste of Japan. Ingredients: Filtered Water, Live Kombucha Cultures (Organic Ceylon Black Tea, Organic Gunpowder Green Tea, Cane Sugar), Yuzu Juice and Zest.
